                            'Dodecagon'  1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" Dodecagon " link play} is a Workbench game where the goal is to link all 12
tiles with each other on a dodecagon shaped board, making a total of
66 links. The least amount of moves it takes to complete the game,
the better it is... there are no restriction, you can move on already
linked tiles or links anytime you like...

  Have fun!

